   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-a" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, I've only heard about it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-d" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Of course. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>The last path taken by the gladiators is none other than the Colosseum. Do you know about the Colosseum?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-b" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are there any restrictions?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I see. Then I'll tell you what I know. First, click the Channel button at the top right corner of the screen and select Colosseum channel to enter Colosseum.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-c" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR><FONT color=#a94407>Minimum level of entry</FONT> is <FONT color=#a82424>Level 10</FONT>, but you would have no problem, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. There are no restrictions other than that. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-e" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>When you enter the <FONT color=#a94407>Colosseum</FONT>, there will be a store where you can buy stuff with the medals you won as Colosseum reward, and a gate you can use to enter the Colosseum. Go through that gate and you can take part in various matches in Colosseum.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-e" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well, yeah.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>Wow you already know about it. You must be really interested. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-f" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Combo practice mode?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>Since you've come all the way here, why don't you try testing how your skills will fare in the Colosseum? I heard that <FONT color=#a82424>[Combo Practice Mode]</FONT> has been newly added to the Colosseum.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-g" mid="57" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="56"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>
Yes. It's a place where all the gladiators practice their own powerful combos. You wouldn't become a great gladiator if you can't master your combos.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-1-h" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>Now try practicing your own combo at <FONT color=#a82424>Combo Practice Mode</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I wish you good luck. Click [Create Room] at Colosseum and select Combo Practice Room in the map.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>So this is Colosseum. I'm thrilled to be standing here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>There's Channel button at the top right corner of the screen. Click on the Channel button and select Colosseum to enter.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-a" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Huh? What are you doing here?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>So this is the Colosseum.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-b" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He even took leave...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I'm on leave to see you in Colosseum, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR>
I was just going to watch you from the spectator's seat but somehow I came all the way down here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-c" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It's nothing.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I could fulfill my dreams like this. Though I'm not here as a gladiator, I still feel overwhelmed to be standing at the Colosseum. This is all thanks to you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-d" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So, that shadow monster...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>Well, I should finish my explanations. This is the last stage before entering the Colosseum. It's <FONT color=#a82424>Combo Practice Mode</FONT>. Here, you can try practicing your combos or experiment with new ones, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-e" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Got it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>
Yes, Colosseums are for duels between heroes. You will need combos that are different from the ones you used for attacking big monsters. So I heard that this practice mode would prepare you for such duels. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1019_guard_roy-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1019_guard_roy-3-f" mid="63" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well this is unnecessary...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>
You're going to be one step closer to becoming the best gladiator. Thank you for helping me realise my dream. This is what I have been collecting for my dream. Since I don't need it anymore, I will give it to you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
